title: Sister Rosetta Tharpe Discography 1956-2011 (18 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
SISTER ROSETTA THARPE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 18 releases...

 * 1956 - Gospel Train
 * 1960 - Live In 1960
 * 1971 - Gospel, Blues And Spirituals - With The Downtown Sisters
 * 1992 - Live At The Hot Club De France
 * 1996 - Complete Recorded Works
 * 1998 - Complete Sister Rosetta Tharpe, Vol 1 - 1938-1943
 * 1998 - Precious Memories
 * 2000 - Complete Sister Rosetta Tharpe, Vol 2 - 1943-1947
 * 2003 - Complete Sister Rosetta Tharpe, Vol 3 - 1947-1951
 * 2005 - Complete Sister Rosetta Tharpe, Vol 4 - 1951-1953
 * 2005 - From Blues To Gospel
 * 2005 - Gospel Train
 * 2005 - The Original Soul Sister
 * 2007 - Gospel Feeling - Live At The Hot Club De France
 * 2008 - Complete Sister Rosetta Tharpe, Vol 5 - 1953-1957
 * 2009 - Gospel N Soul Revival
 * 2010 - Blessed Assurance
 * 2011 - Complete Sister Rosetta Tharpe, Vol 6 - 1958-1959

Sister Rosetta Tharpe was an American singer, songwriter, guitarist and recording artist. A pioneer of twentieth-century music, Tharpe attained great popularity in the 1930s and 1940s with her gospel recordings that were a unique mixture of spiritual lyrics and rhythmic/early rock accompaniment.

For Him,
TorrentTracts - December 2013
